code: @Override public boolean isValidChange(OperationMode nextMode) {     return nextMode == RUNNING. }
@Override public boolean isValidChange(OperationMode nextMode) {     return nextMode == RUNNING || nextMode == STOPPED. }
@Override public boolean isValidChange(OperationMode nextMode) {     return nextMode == STOPPING. }

static OperationMode fromString(String string) {     return EnumSet.allOf(OperationMode.class).stream().filter(e -> string.equalsIgnoreCase(e.name())).findFirst().orElseThrow(() -> new IllegalArgumentException(String.format(Locale.ROOT, "%s is not a valid operation_mode", string))). }
